{"tid":1743482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【每日七篇】中共兩日14次抗議《人權法》","createTime":"2019-11-21T08:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T09:27:03.000Z","uid":285559,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"07483ad9d7265b530da9b746f65d3346b9758e7c","tid":1743482,"uid":285559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:18:57.000Z","msg":"11/20:<br />\n外交部發言人<strong>耿爽</strong>就美國國會參議院通過&ldquo;香港人權與民主法案&rdquo;發表談話<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web/fyrbt_673021/t1717260.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fmprc.gov.cn%2Fweb%2Ffyrbt_673021%2Ft1717260.shtml&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameCtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=a1037f38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web/fyrbt_673021/t1717260.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港中聯辦</strong>就美國參議院通過所謂&ldquo;2019年香港人權與民主法案&rdquo;發表聲明<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.xinhuanet.com/2019-11/20/c_1125252497.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xinhuanet.com%2F2019-11%2F20%2Fc_1125252497.htm&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameCtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=9ec37fcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.xinhuanet.com/2019-11/20/c_1125252497.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n國務院港澳辦強烈抗議和譴責美國國會參議院通過&ldquo;香港人權與民主法案&rdquo; (<strong>新聞發言人楊光</strong>)<br />\n<a href=\"http://xinhuanet.com/2019-11/20/c_1125252485.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fxinhuanet.com%2F2019-11%2F20%2Fc_1125252485.htm&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameCtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=ffb53713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://xinhuanet.com/2019-11/20/c_1125252485.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>全國人大外事委員會</strong>就美國國會參議院通過&ldquo;2019年香港人權與民主法案&rdquo;發表聲明<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.xinhuanet.com/2019-11/20/c_1125252668.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xinhuanet.com%2F2019-11%2F20%2Fc_1125252668.htm&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameCtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=30cc9153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.xinhuanet.com/2019-11/20/c_1125252668.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>外交部駐港公署</strong>負責人強烈譴責美參議院通過涉港議案<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.xinhuanet.com/2019-11/20/c_1125253451.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xinhuanet.com%2F2019-11%2F20%2Fc_1125253451.htm&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameCtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=554f20b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.xinhuanet.com/2019-11/20/c_1125253451.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>全國政協外事委員會</strong>就美國國會參議院通過&ldquo;香港人權與民主法案&rdquo;發表聲明<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.xinhuanet.com/2019-11/20/c_1125252681.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xinhuanet.com%2F2019-11%2F20%2Fc_1125252681.htm&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameCtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=06c3179c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.xinhuanet.com/2019-11/20/c_1125252681.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>特區政府</strong>回應美國參議院通過涉港法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201911/20/P2019112000034.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201911%2F20%2FP2019112000034.htm&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameCtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=6c93531b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201911/20/P2019112000034.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局局長會見傳媒開場發言（只有中文） (<strong>商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華</strong>)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201911/20/P2019112000412.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201911%2F20%2FP2019112000412.htm&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameCtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=3a746bf0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201911/20/P2019112000412.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n外交部召見美國駐華使館負責人就美國會參議院通過涉港法案提出嚴正交涉 (<strong>中國外交部副部長馬朝旭</strong>)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.xinhuanet.com/politics/2019-11/20/c_1125255006.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xinhuanet.com%2Fpolitics%2F2019-11%2F20%2Fc_1125255006.htm&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameCtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=28f3cb77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.xinhuanet.com/politics/2019-11/20/c_1125255006.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n新華社評論員：美方乾預中國內政的圖謀絕不會得逞<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.xinhuanet.com/gangao/2019-11/20/c_1125254978.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xinhuanet.com%2Fgangao%2F2019-11%2F20%2Fc_1125254978.htm&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameCtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=d2f1c2b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.xinhuanet.com/gangao/2019-11/20/c_1125254978.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n11/21:<br />\n<br />\n<strong>外交部駐港公署特派員謝鋒</strong>召見美國駐港總領事就美參議院通過涉港法案提出強烈抗議<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.xinhuanet.com/2019-11/21/c_1125255572.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xinhuanet.com%2F2019-11%2F21%2Fc_1125255572.htm&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameCtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=f3f9d5e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.xinhuanet.com/2019-11/21/c_1125255572.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>特區政府</strong>期望美國政府謹慎處理涉港法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201911/21/P2019112100313.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201911%2F21%2FP2019112100313.htm&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameCtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=855c5570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201911/21/P2019112100313.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>王毅</strong>見美前防長：美出台干涉中國內政法案損互信<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2502809\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2502809&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameCtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=7a4e70d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2502809</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>陳茂波</strong>指香港人權與民主法案損害美國利益<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20191121130348\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20191121130348&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameCtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlE